籤詩版本二:
Kunyange ukadzima moto nehuni, zvinhu zvose zvichapfuta, uye kunyange ukapisa kane zviuru zvitatu, zvichaitika zvakare.
Kana iwe uine hanya nekubwinya uye hupfumi, zviri nani kuchenesa iyo yakarasika kuedza
詩意:
Hexagram iyi yakafanana nekubata huni kuti udzime moto.
Ngwarira pazvinhu zvose.
解曰: Kune zviuru zvezvirongwa. Kumbodenha. Zviri nani kusafamba. Kutya kukonzera dambudziko.
籤詩故事一:
◇Chibi Hondo
Munguva yeHumambo Hutatu, mauto aCao Cao aive akamira pamahombekombe eChibi.
Mukuru weSun Quan Zhou Yu akabatanidza uto raLiu Bei kurwisa Cao Cao.
Kongming akatora mukana wemhepo yekumabvazuva, uye Huang Gai akaisa moto kuchikepe chetani, uye mauto maviri akarwa zvakasimba.
Paiva negungwa remoto, uye hondo yaCao yakakundwa. Nhoroondo yaizivikanwa seHondo yeChibi.
◎ Cherechedza:
鏖, ruzha rwunonzi ㄠˊ. Zvinoreva kuti paive nevakawanda vakafa muhondo yakaoma iyi.
